                                <h1>Ghettos</h1>
                                <p>The map below shows the locations of Jewish ghettos established during the war. This is not a comprehensive listing of ghettos&mdash;only those which specifically pertain to the interviews in this collection are included.</p><p>Click on a location to view details about each ghetto and links to corresponding interviews.</p>
